                in the corporate and social sector and is the co-founder of Drug Aid Africa Initiative.<br><br>
                “Osamede, the Stage Play” which is her debut project in the arts is a tool she intends to utilize as an<br>
                avenue to raise the crucial topics of human rights, women’s role in social change, creation of job opportunities<br>
                for youths and to promote the creative arts industry in Nigeria with the strength of her corporate background.<br> 
